musician</link>s, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../262/39262.xml">
playwright</link>s, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../885/23885.xml">
poets</link> and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../ury/23rd_century.xml">
activists</link> recall the struggle against Apartheid from the 1940's to the 1990's, and the important role that music played in that struggle. The documentary uses a mixture of <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../975/236975.xml">
interview</link>s,  musical performances and historical film footage. Among the famous South Africans who take part are <physical_entity wordnetid="100001930" confidence="0.8">
